Return JSON array of tasks:
[{"task":"Concise %s summary","requester":"","assignee":"","assigned_at":"","source_ts":"EXTRACT_EXACT_ID_FROM_PROMPT","deadline":"date/time","category":"todo|waiting|promise"}]
